snippet.textDisplay:
Now comes the official game on PS4,Switch,XboxOne & PC
Dark Crystal Age of Resistance Tactics.
Being released on February 4th 2020.
The game looks great, It's like the classic game Final Fantasy Tactics (PSX & PSP) except now it's The Dark Crystal Character's,Lore,Vehicles,World and so on!
It's really going to be a great game.
I don't foresee Netflix reprising season 2 but rather the game from what i can tell is essentially continuing where season 1 left off considering there are three publisher's of the Game Jim Henson Games, Netflix Games & Bonus XP.
I have no problem with that I'm just glad We finally will have a Dark Crystal game some thirty odd some years later!
But like the saying goes better late than never!
Also I believe the game supports 4 player Co-Op Local & via Wi-Fi.

Now keep your fingers crossed they don't ruin or destroy the upcoming Labyrinth sequel film already in the work's!
